{"tid":1557672,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"《睇黎港共想暗地裡大屠殺》","createTime":"2019-09-10T08:12:11.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-20T16:32:39.000Z","uid":49898,"like":134,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":38,"replies":[{"pid":"f8d0fca2a19800e6e1ffba174be2fcb7fa51f4b8","tid":1557672,"uid":49898,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-10T08:12:11.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.hk01.com/article/373490?utm_medium=Social&amp;utm_source=telegram&amp;utm_campaign=mama\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hk01.com%2Farticle%2F373490%3Futm_medium%3DSocial%26utm_source%3Dtelegram%26utm_campaign%3Dmama&d=SMAvs7Hy8J1z03%2F%2B44sdD02FGjryiJR74P7%2B0uEOyUg%3D&h=fd1d29db\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.hk01.com/article/373490?utm_medium=Social&amp;utm_source=telegram&amp;utm_campaign=mama</a><br />\n<br />\n話俾休班警喎，平時已經無委任證又無樣<br />\n到時又唔知真實會派幾多枝，同埋有咩人攞得<br />\n<br />\n平時開完槍先舉旗，打完人又唔係拘捕<br />\n你話實行左會有咩事發生？<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">例子1</span></span><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.hk01.com/突發/363941/油麻地劏房揭命案-23歲男手腳被綁膠袋笠頭-警調查指無可疑\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hk01.com%2F%E7%AA%81%E7%99%BC%2F363941%2F%E6%B2%B9%E9%BA%BB%E5%9C%B0%E5%8A%8F%E6%88%BF%E6%8F%AD%E5%91%BD%E6%A1%88-23%E6%AD%B2%E7%94%B7%E6%89%8B%E8%85%B3%E8%A2%AB%E7%B6%81%E8%86%A0%E8%A2%8B%E7%AC%A0%E9%A0%AD-%E8%AD%A6%E8%AA%BF%E6%9F%A5%E6%8C%87%E7%84%A1%E5%8F%AF%E7%96%91&d=SMAvs7Hy8J1z03%2F%2B44sdD02FGjryiJR74P7%2B0uEOyUg%3D&h=bf5d4482\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.hk01.com/突發/363941/油麻地劏房揭命案-23歲男手腳被綁膠袋笠頭-警調查指無可疑</a><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">例子2</span></span><br />\n‪身纏膠籃藏磚頭　老翁雙手被綁浮屍北角　家中檢遺書 (18:00) - 20190907 - 港聞 - 即時新聞 - 明報新聞網 <a href=\"https://shar.es/aXdYsf‬\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fshar.es%2FaXdYsf%E2%80%AC&d=SMAvs7Hy8J1z03%2F%2B44sdD02FGjryiJR74P7%2B0uEOyUg%3D&h=5f0fef61\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://shar.es/aXdYsf‬</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n宜家香港已經<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">進入左緊急狀態</span></span><br />\n大家夜晚唔好出街<br />\n200萬人入夜就留屋企<br />\n<br />\n班港豬藍屍仲未知死<br />\n我地就將白色恐怖帶俾佢地<br />\n晚晚都722元朗屯門咁<br />\n<br />\n依排咁多外媒<br />\n俾佢地報香港唔再馬照跑舞照跳<br />\n宜家已經正式成為<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">中國香港市</span></span>"},{"pid":"78e091a14e419f8489fed84c2df54257049f3b32","tid":1557672,"uid":225130,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-10T08:12:52.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"d3d55cefd085a4af7e2af06fb6c5c2d88dec82c3","tid":1557672,"uid":227929,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-10T08:13:02.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"d2404d7dd2e07f4431e0d50f451390dc4bbc6ac0","tid":1557672,"uid":118120,"like":33,"dislike":0,"score":33,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2019-09-10T08:13:20.000Z","msg":"而家香港根本就係內戰狀態<br />\n警察只要隨便搵個藉口就可以無差別打人, 仲要打錯人, 打死人都唔洗負責<br />\n呢d 唔係內戰係咩"},{"pid":"e4d95662db4ecb751b00b2bcdec40ed1587bce6a","tid":1557672,"uid":288523,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-10T08:14:54.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"fdf4923d59e62846bdf6eb2ca1f8086a1d2042f0","tid":1557672,"uid":49898,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"d2404d7dd2e07f4431e0d50f451390dc4bbc6ac0","tid":1557672,"uid":118120,"like":33,"dislike":0,"score":33,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2019-09-10T08:13:20.000Z","msg":"而家香港根本就係內戰狀態<br />\n警察只要隨便搵個藉口就可以無差別打人, 仲要打錯人, 打死人都唔洗負責<br />\n呢d 唔係內戰係咩"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-10T08:16:04.000Z","msg":"係，但好多仲係hea下hea下咁<br />\n根本情況越黎越嚴峻"},{"pid":"49470e5d653158edc6173c9c2f795d6e2bd0e399","tid":1557672,"uid":49898,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-10T08:16:50.000Z","msg":"仲有新屋嶺 831<br />\n我地一定要搵到真相"},{"pid":"206153773c3a9660ce3cb01eaa8a58629b3c71bb","tid":1557672,"uid":146737,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-10T08:17:20.000Z","msg":"推<br />\n<br />\n針對中立淺藍黃嘅文宣